*显示文件的详细信息：
$ stat patch_files 
输入之后，输出如下：
File: `patch_files'
Size: 3500            Blocks: 8          IO Block: 4096   regular file
Device: 802h/2050d      Inode: 44568       Links: 1
Access: (0777/-rwxrwxrwx)  Uid: (    0/    root)   Gid: (    0/    root)
Access: 2009-08-24 11:26:20.000000000 +0800
Modify: 2009-08-24 11:26:20.000000000 +0800
Change: 2009-08-24 11:26:20.000000000 +0800
这里，如果文件不存在则输出错误信息。
